desc: This project is a fully functional music player built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to play, pause, and navigate through a collection of songs with ease, providing an intuitive and engaging audio experience.
This application provides comprehensive information about any country in the world. By searching for a country, users can access detailed data and see the country's location on a world map.
This project is a dynamic e-commerce webpage where users can browse products, add items to their cart, and remove items as needed. Click on cart button to see their products.
This project is a fully responsive landing page. The page provides an engaging and seamless user experience across all devices, showcasing the company's services and values.

A responsive password generator application designed to create secure and random passwords for users. It ensures strong security by generating passwords that can include a mix of letters, numbers, and special characters.

This project is a fully responsive UI clone of the Blue Origin landing page. It replicates the design and layout of Blue Origin's official site, showcasing the company's mission, services, and achievements with high fidelity.

This project is a fully responsive UI clone of the Starlink landing page. It faithfully replicates the design and layout of Starlink's official site, highlighting the company's mission, services, and technological innovations.
